Pre-processed data¶

cimr-d distribution includes pre-processed data. These are provided as examples for analyses using cimr. All license and copyrights are reserved for the original producer / distributer of data. Citations and relevant metadata are available in respective documentations.

Useful links: Data repository | Citations | Issues & Ideas
